dc_title_s: Map showing the boulevards and park system and twelve miles of lake frontage of the city of Chicago
dc_description_s: Subject: Map of the city of Chicago, Illinois, with concentric circles from the center of the city. Shows streets, railroads, parks and other points of interest.|Cover title: Rand, McNally & Co.'s official map of the city of Chicago indexed ...; "Entered according to act of Congress in the year 1884, by Rand, McNally & Co., in the office of the Librarian of Congress, at Washington, D.C."; Includes index to streets and avenues.|58 x 43 centimeters|Scale approximately 1:118,800|City Maps
